    "Topic modelingKeypoint-based summarization (KeyBERT) is a pre-trained model that uses BERT embeddings to extract the most relevant keywords or key phrases from a given document.",
    "KeyBERT is a powerful tool for summarizing text and can be used to generate topic names for articles, among other applications [46].",
    "In this methodology, we will outline how to use the KeyBERT model to extract keywords to be used as a topic name for an article.",
